:PortaDOOM - <github.com/Kroc/PortaDOOM>
:===============================================================================
_PortaDOOM_ is the work of <Kroc Camen> and contributors and made possible only by the awesomeness of the `DOOM` community.

The WADs distributed with _PortaDOOM_ may not match their original source downloads (i.e. checksum) due to extra compression applied by _DOOM-Crusher_, a tool for automatically optimizing WAD files and resources:
_github.com/Kroc/DOOM-Crusher_.

